mxCell.value: Mapper Run On-Demand to Edit XML

PowerSlate Overview
Revised 2020-02-15
by Wyatt Best

Task Scheduler passes location of JSON config file as command-line argument. Config file contains locations of everything else (Slate web services, SQL databases, recruiterMapping.xml, SMPT).

"Active" Slate Source Format fires rules, but "Passive" does not.

Python wrappers handle errors, which are sent via email from sync_ondemand or to browser from sync_http.
